Description of problem:
In Debian, devscripts ships with a hand full of symlinks to ease its use [1]. Those symlinks are currently missing from the Fedora package. People (and scripts) are used to the symlinks present in Debian and might wonder about their absence in Fedora.

[1] http://sources.debian.net/src/devscripts/2.15.5/debian/links/


Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
f21, devscripts-2.15.4-1.fc21.x86_64
affects later versions too

How reproducible:
always

Steps to Reproduce:
1. install devscripts
2. run "dch"

Actual results:
There is no dch executable

Expected results:
debchange gets started
